&gt; junit-platform-console project.
&gt; 6.1.1. Discovering Tests
&gt; 
&gt; Having test discovery as a dedicated feature of the platform itself
&gt; frees IDEs and build tools from most of the difficulties they had to
&gt; go through to identify test classes and test methods in previous
&gt; versions of JUnit.
